headline: Travel and Vacation Providers Stocks Q2 Recap: Benchmarking United Airlines (NASDAQ:UAL)
summary: Earnings results often indicate what direction a company will take in the months ahead. With Q2 behind us, let’s have a look at United Airlines (NASDAQ:UAL) and its peers.
